# .vouchignore — Strategic Ignorance Configuration
# Files and patterns excluded from Cognitive Debt calculation
#
# These are files that, by design, no human is expected to review
# or endorse. Excluding them is not gaming the metric — it's being
# honest about where human comprehension delivers value.

# Dependency lock files (Alien Code — autonomous updates)
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml
Cargo.lock
go.sum
Gemfile.lock
composer.lock
poetry.lock

# Auto-generated clients and SDKs
src/generated/**
**/generated/**
**/*.pb.go
**/*.g.dart
**/*_gen.go
**/*.generated.*

# Massive data fixtures and snapshots
__snapshots__/
test/fixtures/**/*.json
test/fixtures/**/*.xml
**/*.snap

# Build artifacts and compiled output
dist/
build/
out/
*.min.js
*.min.css
*.bundle.*

# Documentation (endorse the code, not the docs)
docs/
*.md
LICENSE
